metadata.name: Post-Apocalyptic Wanderer
metadata.description: "Bravely braving the dusty streets, this mighty mammoth takes on the elements with a gas mask firmly in place. Whether navigating a post-apocalyptic wasteland or simply surviving the everyday grind, this resilient creature is ready to take on whatever comes its way. So why wait? Join the ranks of the unstoppable and let the world know you're not afraid to get a little dirty."
